            "content": "### Goal\nGenerate all pagination URLs and filter them for downstream processing..\n\n### What To Do\n1. Run **Manual Scraper** to retrieve the total number of pagination pages.\n2. Filter the results and transform the base URL into paginated URLs.\n\n### Output\nComplete list of pagination URLs."
